{"task_id": "task_104_28_landmark_photo_identification", "category": "104_multimodal", "task_yaml": {"task_id": "task_104_28_landmark_photo_identification", "category": "104_multimodal", "agent_sys": "openclaw", "agent_id": "main", "model": "gpt-5.4", "timeout_seconds": 1200, "max_total_seconds": 1800, "success_threshold": 0.9, "recording": "none", "headed": "auto", "task": "`/tmp_workspace/clawbench/sources/travel_photos/` contains 30 travel photos with random filenames.\nEach image shows a real-world landmark.\n\nPlease identify the following for each photo, one by one:\n- Landmark name\n- City\n- Country\n\nRequirements:\n1. Process all 30 images in this directory, without omissions or duplicates.\n2. Output the final results to `/tmp_workspace/results/landmark_report.csv`. The CSV header must be:\n   `file_name,landmark,city,country`\n3. Preserve the original filenames, and write the CSV sorted by `file_name`.\n4. Also write `/tmp_workspace/results/landmark_summary.md` with a brief summary:\n   - The 10 images you are most confident about, each with the original `file_name`, identification result,\n     and visible evidence\n   - The 3 images you think are easiest to confuse, each with the original `file_name`, possible confusion\n     target, and distinguishing evidence\n5. If you are not completely certain about an individual image, still give your most likely answer; do not leave it blank.\n", "sources": ["travel_photos/"], "codex": {"max_user_followups": 2}}, "prompt": "`/tmp_workspace/clawbench/sources/travel_photos/` contains 30 travel photos with random filenames.\nEach image shows a real-world landmark.\n\nPlease identify the following for each photo, one by one:\n- Landmark name\n- City\n- Country\n\nRequirements:\n1. Process all 30 images in this directory, without omissions or duplicates.\n2. Output the final results to `/tmp_workspace/results/landmark_report.csv`. The CSV header must be:\n   `file_name,landmark,city,country`\n3. Preserve the original filenames, and write the CSV sorted by `file_name`.\n4. Also write `/tmp_workspace/results/landmark_summary.md` with a brief summary:\n   - The 10 images you are most confident about, each with the original `file_name`, identification result,\n     and visible evidence\n   - The 3 images you think are easiest to confuse, each with the original `file_name`, possible confusion\n     target, and distinguishing evidence\n5. If you are not completely certain about an individual image, still give your most likely answer; do not leave it blank.\n", "eval_rule_md": "", "assets": {"privacy": null, "skills": null, "sources": [{"name": "travel_photos", "path": "travel_photos", "is_dir": true, "children": [{"name": "0jj4nac6crjgvu.jpg", "path": "travel_photos/0jj4nac6crjgvu.jpg", "is_dir": false, "size": 443387, "url": "http://100.116.9.115:9018/injection/104_multimodal/task_104_28_landmark_photo_identification/sources/travel_photos/0jj4nac6crjgvu.jpg"}, {"name": "0we0ech08qejhn.jpg", "path": "travel_photos/0we0ech08qejhn.jpg", "is_dir": false, "size": 369120, "url": "http://100.116.9.115:9018/injection/104_multimodal/task_104_28_landmark_photo_identification/sources/travel_photos/0we0ech08qejhn.jpg"}, {"name": "0z4nwcsdof6gn0.jpg", "path": "travel_photos/0z4nwcsdof6gn0.jpg", "is_dir": false, "size": 506490, "url": "http://100.116.9.115:9018/injection/104_multimodal/task_104_28_landmark_photo_identification/sources/travel_photos/0z4nwcsdof6gn0.jpg"}, {"name": "2emaapje1hgx8l.jpg", "path": "travel_photos/2emaapje1hgx8l.jpg", "is_dir": false, "size": 369253, "url": "http://100.116.9.115:9018/injection/104_multimodal/task_104_28_landmark_photo_identification/sources/travel_photos/2emaapje1hgx8l.jpg"}, {"name": "35dot43ize3bgv.jpg", "path": "travel_photos/35dot43ize3bgv.jpg", "is_dir": false, "size": 383999, "url": "http://100.116.9.115:9018/injection/104_multimodal/task_104_28_landmark_photo_identification/sources/travel_photos/35dot43ize3bgv.jpg"}, {"name": "6ww8ewocfkd49a.jpg",